(52) Transon's E Infusion - 580hp healed for 275mana<br>
(60) Transon's E Renewal - 900hp healed for 400mana<br>
(64) Planar Renewal - 1200hp healed for 300mana<br>
<br>
Planar renewal is already a great heal spell, and much better (and far easier to obtain) than the lvl 60 heal spell that every magician under the sun moans about not getting.  While spectral parchments dont grow on trees or rain down from the sky, they're far more common than a possible drop off Grieg, a boss rarely killed nowadays.  So put in your time, wish for a bit of luck, and you'll get Planar Renewal.  I got it the first time i handed in a Spectral Parchment.  Its a great spell, and along with the new pets that regen for 3-5% / tic, there is no need for a pet CH*<br>
<br>
